lead_paragraph: THE HAGUE, Sept. 9.--The Minister of the Interior, M. Thorbecke, is at this moment upon a tour of observation through the country, preliminary to the opening of the parliamentary session on Monday next. He has been received by the people with lively demonstrations of respect and sympathy.
